flowchart TD
    START((Baslangic)) --> DISCOVER[Urun/Hizmet Kesfet]
    DISCOVER --> BROWSE[Kategori/Arama ile Gez]
    BROWSE --> DETAIL[Detay Incele]
    DETAIL --> DECIDE{Satin Alma Karari}

    DECIDE -->|Hayir| BROWSE
    DECIDE -->|Evet| CART[Sepete Ekle]

    CART --> MORE{Baska Urun?}
    MORE -->|Evet| BROWSE
    MORE -->|Hayir| CHECKOUT[Odeme Sayfasi]

    CHECKOUT --> AUTH{Giris Yapti mi?}
    AUTH -->|Hayir| LOGIN[Giris / Kayit]
    AUTH -->|Evet| ADDRESS[Adres Sec/Ekle]
    LOGIN --> ADDRESS

    ADDRESS --> PAYMENT[Odeme Yontemi Sec]
    PAYMENT --> CONFIRM{Siparisi Onayla}
    CONFIRM -->|Iptal| CART
    CONFIRM -->|Onayla| PROCESS[Odeme Isle]

    PROCESS --> RESULT{Odeme Sonucu}
    RESULT -->|Basarisiz| PAYMENT
    RESULT -->|Basarili| ORDER_CREATED[Siparis Olusturuldu]

    ORDER_CREATED --> NOTIFY[Bildirim Gonder]
    NOTIFY --> PREPARE[Siparis Hazirla]
    PREPARE --> SHIP[Kargoya Ver]
    SHIP --> DELIVER[Teslim Et]
    DELIVER --> FEEDBACK{Degerlendirme?}
    FEEDBACK -->|Evet| REVIEW[Yorum Yaz]
    FEEDBACK -->|Hayir| END_OK((Bitis))
    REVIEW --> END_OK
